<br>
Also supposedly (per the Ranger Glade) a ranger can do more damage with a good 2hb than with dual wielding epics. Good 2hb i mean like the one that drops in KC. Cant think of the name right now though. <br>
<br>
I believe warriors and knights get the damage bonus bonus(yes double bonus) on 2hs. Where rangers, druids, and shaman get it on 2hb. I know on my ranger the damage bonus was double with 2hb over 2hs.<br>
